Collecting three months of highlights on Armin van Buuren's radio show A State of Trance, is the latest Radio Top 20! Armin's September, October and November favourites unite in this must-have pack for fans. Including tunes by Orjan Nilsen, John O'Callaghan, Ferry Corsten, Nic Chagall, Dash Berlin, Craig Connelly, The Thrillseekers and many more, it brings you the Future Favourites, Tunes of the Week and anything else that has been ASOT approved!
